Bug 2053894 - Fix 'Search online' checkbox always resetting to unchecked in Virtual Folder Properties. r=mkmelin

The port of bug 2008041 (d89f225042b2) incorrectly moved the
checkbox.checked = false assignment outside of the conditional in
updateOnlineSearchState(). This caused the checkbox to be unchecked
every time the dialog opens, even when online search was available.

Restore the original logic: only clear the checkbox when there are
no online servers (i.e., when it's disabled).

Add a test that verifies the checkbox state is preserved across
dialog opens when online servers are in the search folders.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D311485


